great to see many online things happening but I also felt a bit isolated but one very positive effect for me was that there were more online workshops as well for example Rishama Shaikh who is speaking later today she started organizing the first scikit-learn online sprint and it was supposed to be in New York and because of the pandemic she made it online and I remember being really excited i was like oh cool i can i can actually take part so i signed up and i have been involved with four more online sprints organized by data umbrella and recently the first in-person psychic learn sprint in paris and yeah it's been great like it has opened the door for me to participate in these events that i otherwise wouldn't have been able to participate

